<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔把袋子扔在桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多金币从袋子里掉了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他笑了笑，然后开始数金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一，二，三......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔把金币一个一个叠放起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克看着金币越来越高。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔继续数着金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“二十六......三十一......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来，他越数越慢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“五十二......五十八......六十六......</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼......呼......呼......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79546</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔打起了呼噜，房子也震动了起来 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是现在！”杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是时候逃跑了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克从烤箱里跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他四处看了看， 没有看到食人魔的妻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克踮起脚尖，慢慢走向桌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔还在打着呼噜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克轻轻地爬上了椅子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克一把抓起一袋金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他快速地跑了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他背着金币继续往前跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望食人魔不要醒来！”杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑几步就回头看一看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160291</EndMilliseconds>
