  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向下看了看，只能看到云层。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下去的路可真长啊！”杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克的心跳得很快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他紧紧地抓住袋子，爬上豆茎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
